query:
insert into nft (
                id,
                address, 
                collection, 
                owner, 
                manager, 
                updated, 
                owner_update_lt, 
                manager_update_lt
            )
            select
                unnest($1::numeric[]),
                unnest($2::varchar[]),
                unnest($3::varchar[]), 
                unnest($4::varchar[]), 
                unnest($5::varchar[]), 
                unnest($6::timestamp[]),
                unnest($7::bigint[]),
                unnest($8::bigint[]) 
            on conflict(address) do nothing
